{"tid":795011,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)房不勝防 2012","createTime":"2018-08-26T16:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T20:00:41.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d1309eccdb1ff8d91c358d96b6b5aefa1042bd","tid":795011,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T16:05:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=d5BHlkYw7QKzR2akVQaPZMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=e55a9daa\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=d5BHlkYw7QKzR2akVQaPZMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7365d033\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=d5BHlkYw7QKzR2akVQaPZMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=1e5ecbae\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/67/Panic_Room_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F6%2F67%2FPanic_Room_poster.jpg&h=f017430e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://lh3.ggpht.com/_AV2CM4rAKbs/SwQGwGAukOI/AAAAAAAAY1w/78FuOgsXMS0/s800/2012movie-600x420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flh3.ggpht.com%2F_AV2CM4rAKbs%2FSwQGwGAukOI%2FAAAAAAAAY1w%2F78FuOgsXMS0%2Fs800%2F2012movie-600x420.jpg&h=fdd8c9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.剛離婚的單親母親瑪姬(茱迪科士打飾)與十一歲的女兒莎拉(姬絲妲史釗活飾)搬到紐約市的一所大宅中，開始她們的獨立生活。這所古老大屋最特別的地方是它擁有一間牢不可破的密室。密室內裝有八部閉路電視，監察大宅內的每一角落，另外更設有獨立空調及足夠一個月用的食糧和各類日常用品。瑪姬和女兒從來也沒想過，她們會有一天需要利用這所密室，直至一天晚上，三名持械桿匪竟潛進這所大宅，目的是要尋找一筆隱藏在屋內的巨款。瑪姬與女兒逼不得已逃進這密室，誰不知密室正是匪徒的目標，雙方從此展開一場困獸鬥..<br />\n<br />\n2.2009年，太陽系九大行星經過幾千年的周期後排列成了一條直線，而太陽也進行了一場歷史上規模最大的太陽爆發。此時在地球，印度的梅加登銅礦場（世界最深的礦場），美國地理學家亞德里安&middot;哈姆斯里來到礦場接見了自己身爲天文地理學家的朋友薩特南，而薩特南卻爲亞德里安展示了一個驚人的事實：幾天前最大的太陽爆發導致中微子的數量到了無法測量的地步，而中微子甚至也開始對地球進行物理反應，開始加熱地球的核心，也會導致整個板塊全部崩潰！亞德里安一回華盛頓就去見了白宮參謀長卡爾&middot;安豪賽，卡爾在極爲震驚下而立刻將此事彙報給美國總統湯瑪斯&middot;威爾森。<br />\n<br />\n12 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=d5BHlkYw7QKzR2akVQaPZMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=008bd0a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=d5BHlkYw7QKzR2akVQaPZMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=b6b2aa1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7542763034ff31b100993dbca236ac4b82190e","tid":795011,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T16:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /